        By default, all data lives in <code class="bg-terminal-dim rounded px-1 py-0.5 text-xs text-terminal-cyan">~/.enchanter/</code>.
        Set <code class="bg-terminal-dim rounded px-1 py-0.5 text-xs text-terminal-cyan">ENCHANTER_HOME</code> to point it elsewhere.
